data.description: Great investment or starter home! 3 bedroom 2 bathroom bungalow with 2 car detached garage (23x23) Spacious living room, 3 bedrooms, including a Large Main Floor Master bedroom. Jetted Tub.  Nice Kitchen and dining area offering ample space for family and guests Full basement with living and storage space. Enjoy privacy and outdoor space in your fenced yard, perfect for relaxing and entertaining. 200 Amp electrical Service. New roof 2018 Quick access to both I-69 and I-475, making commuting a breeze. Don’t wait, at this price, Home won’t last long.
